{"tid":1096373,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭俊英明明有錄影「消失在節目」 網友讚：史上最強剪接！","createTime":"2019-04-07T16:07:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T17:23:40.000Z","uid":74065,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"eca1e84ac5713d185514f8dbf7a67ffd7acd7544","tid":1096373,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:07:22.000Z","msg":"南韓歌手鄭俊英3月中被抓到偷拍、散播性愛片，如今已遭警方逮補移送檢察機關。然而，他出事前活躍在各種節目拍攝，無辜牽連許多節目，其中一個包含旅遊實境《窮遊豪華團》，製作方無奈表示「儘可能減少其畫面」，直到6日再度播岀，有觀眾發現鄭俊英已經完全消失在鏡頭前，令許多網友讚嘆：「史上最強剪接！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4010/d4010082.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4010%2Fd4010082.jpg&h=820bb1bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼鄭俊英消失在節目《窮遊豪華團》，網友讚「史上最強剪接」。（圖／翻攝自tvN）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4010/d4010080.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4010%2Fd4010080.jpg&h=c02eb6c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《窮遊豪華團》主持群哈妮、朴明洙、文世潤、鄭俊英等人於2月前往土耳其伊斯坦堡拍攝，怎料，節目都拍完了，鄭俊英卻被爆出偷拍性愛片，害節目組剪接必須重頭來過。《窮遊豪華團》6日播岀土耳其旅遊篇首集，鄭俊英竟神奇地消失在節目中，後製組以特大的字幕效果或者將畫面切成兩半，營造出鄭俊英沒參與錄製的效果，令大批網友讚嘆連連「節目辛苦了」、「真的完全沒出現」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4010/d4010081.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4010%2Fd4010081.jpg&h=0c84b65e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲節目《窮遊豪華團》裡看不到鄭俊英的身影。（圖／翻攝自tvN）<br />\n<br />\n鄭俊英出事前活躍在藝能圈，老牌節目《2天1夜》曾寫下不少感人故事，定期邀請大咖如朴寶劍下鄉，都能創造話題，卻因他的問題，節目暫停播岀，且極有可能未來都永遠不會再次上架，全面禁播，令不少粉絲惋惜"},{"pid":"710a6dd7ed2b19d6c7d9da535b5d9b61b22c0ceb","tid":1096373,"uid":74561,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:10:30.000Z","msg":"拍攝途中唔知有無食埋Hana"},{"pid":"78604c450c8b68b5d51ead4f353ea3c06e3a14a2","tid":1096373,"uid":74065,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"710a6dd7ed2b19d6c7d9da535b5d9b61b22c0ceb","tid":1096373,"uid":74561,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:10:30.000Z","msg":"拍攝途中唔知有無食埋Hana"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:11:31.000Z","msg":"HANI碎花生GIF"},{"pid":"0a4d1c0aca296652caa0e2d30aa97623e6f0883e","tid":1096373,"uid":3405,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"710a6dd7ed2b19d6c7d9da535b5d9b61b22c0ceb","tid":1096373,"uid":74561,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:10:30.000Z","msg":"拍攝途中唔知有無食埋Hana"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:18:52.000Z","msg":"邊撚個HANA<br />\n<img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/images/0466286ca36748dce582d06bf77e86ca/tenor.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.tenor.com%2Fimages%2F0466286ca36748dce582d06bf77e86ca%2Ftenor.gif&h=7705c47d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ecd4fe64bef81dd18a36855d7b5bbb26746370d","tid":1096373,"uid":213300,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"0a4d1c0aca296652caa0e2d30aa97623e6f0883e","tid":1096373,"uid":3405,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"710a6dd7ed2b19d6c7d9da535b5d9b61b22c0ceb","tid":1096373,"uid":74561,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:10:30.000Z","msg":"拍攝途中唔知有無食埋Hana"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:18:52.000Z","msg":"邊撚個HANA<br />\n<img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/images/0466286ca36748dce582d06bf77e86ca/tenor.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.tenor.com%2Fimages%2F0466286ca36748dce582d06bf77e86ca%2Ftenor.gif&h=7705c47d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:24:14.000Z","msg":"菊梓喬"},{"pid":"b4834a796b7d04cd68782890341a7774aefea350","tid":1096373,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a4d1c0aca296652caa0e2d30aa97623e6f0883e","tid":1096373,"uid":3405,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"710a6dd7ed2b19d6c7d9da535b5d9b61b22c0ceb","tid":1096373,"uid":74561,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:10:30.000Z","msg":"拍攝途中唔知有無食埋Hana"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:18:52.000Z","msg":"邊撚個HANA<